         <div class="h-entry">
          <div class="panel-heading">
           <h2 class="p-name">
            <a class="u-url u-uid" href="https://uphys.msu.edu/resources/hepatitis-a-southeast-michigan-outbreak" rel="bookmark">
             Southeast Michigan Hepatitis A Outbreak
            </a>
           </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-body">
           <p class="p-summary">
            Public health officials and the Michigan Department of Health and Human Services (MDHHS) are continuing to see an elevated number of hepatitis A cases in Southeast Michigan.
           </p>
           <div>
            <a class="u-url u-uid more-link" href="https://uphys.msu.edu/resources/hepatitis-a-southeast-michigan-outbreak" rel="bookmark">
